---
layout: "layouts/base.njk"
title: "首页"
header: "partials/header_zh.njk"
lang: zh
---

<section class="bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/assets/Images/Restaurant-1.JPG');">
    <div class="w-full bg-black bg-opacity-50 pb-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center text-white pt-24 md:pt-32">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-display">体验卓越美食</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">在曼德勒市中心开启一段美食之旅。在宜必思尚品曼德勒中心酒店，体验欧亚菜系的完美融合。</p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="/zh/menu/" class="inline-block bg-streats-red text-white px-10 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-red-800 transition duration-300 text-lg font-semibold">
                    查看菜单
                </a>
                <a href="/zh/events/" class="inline-block bg-white text-streats-red px-10 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-streats-red hover:text-white transition duration-300 text-lg font-semibold">
                    预订活动
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="container mx-auto px-6 -mt-16 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900">早餐</h2>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mt-2">自助餐形式</p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-left border-t pt-4">
                <p class="flex justify-between"><strong>住店客人:</strong> <span>免费</span></p>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <p><strong>店外客人:</strong></p>
                    <p class="flex justify-between ml-4"><span>成人:</span> <span>28,500 MMK</span></p>
                    <p class="flex justify-between ml-4"><span>儿童:</span> <span>15,000 MMK</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900">午餐</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 flex-grow">多样化的单点菜单，融合了欧洲和亚洲风味，点亮您的午后时光。</p>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <a href="/zh/menu/" class="font-bold text-streats-red hover:underline">探索午餐菜单 →</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900">晚餐</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 flex-grow">在充满活力的氛围中，享用我们精选的美味佳肴，度过一个难忘的晚餐。</p>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <a href="/zh/menu/" class="font-bold text-streats-red hover:underline">品味晚餐佳肴 →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% if promotions_zh and promotions_zh.length > 0 %}
    <section class="bg-grey-100 py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900">当前优惠</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">不要错过这些特别优惠！</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                {%- for promo in promotions_zh -%}
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="{{ promo.image }}" alt="{{ promo.alt }}" class="w-full h-56 object-cover">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display">{{ promo.title }}</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">{{ promo.description }}</p>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold text-red-700">{{ promo.validity }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% else %}
    <section class="bg-gray-100 pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900">主厨推荐</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">品味我们全年供应的精选佳肴。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                {%- for item in signatures_zh -%}
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
                    <img src="{{ item.image }}" alt="{{ item.name }}" class="w-full h-56 object-cover">
                    <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display">{{ item.name }}</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2 flex-grow">{{ item.description }}</p>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold text-red-700">{{ item.price }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endif %}